itis" data-hovercard='p$t$dermatitis'>皮肤科徐宏俊医生</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">北京大学民航临床医学院</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/er-bi-hou-ke-ke-pu-xiao-yi-sheng" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$er-bi-hou-ke-ke-pu-xiao-yi-sheng'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cf3224f304296871ea58d37c66046c67_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="柏舟"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/guomin/er-bi-hou-ke-ke-pu-xiao-yi-sheng/answers" class="answers text-muted">1 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/er-bi-hou-ke-ke-pu-xiao-yi-sheng" data-hovercard='p$t$er-bi-hou-ke-ke-pu-xiao-yi-sheng'>柏舟</a><div class="bio">耳鼻喉科医生 微信见个人主页详细资料</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/yuxi624" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$yuxi624'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cc27602c6637ff2e1a57abaa77b7d1c6_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="禹汐"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/guomin/yuxi624/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/yuxi624" data-hovercard='p$t$yuxi624'>禹汐</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">中国医科大学附属第一医院皮肤科 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 医师</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/sanjiayifly" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$sanjiayifly'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dec7eb7423f89bb819ed123f26c09068_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="Gigi"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/guomin/sanjiayifly/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/sanjiayifly" data-hovercard='p$t$sanjiayifly'>Gigi</a><div class="bio">L’OREAL CHINA <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 科学家</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/